STATE
v.
Sebastian X. MOORE. No. 409P05-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 26, 2008. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, C. Colon Willoughby, Jr., District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 12th day of June 2008 by Defendant Charging the N.C. Supreme Court to Review Applicable Law Concerning Choice of Counsel:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference this the 26th day of August 2008."
